queryResponse.sql:
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "contract_win_rate_output.price_dat_ratio") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY "contract_win_rate_output.price_dat_ratio" ASC, z__pivot_col_rank) AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "contract_win_rate_output.model_name" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "contract_win_rate_output.model_name") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    contract_win_rate_output."MODEL_NAME"  AS "contract_win_rate_output.model_name",
    contract_win_rate_output."PRICE_DAT_RATIO"  AS "contract_win_rate_output.price_dat_ratio",
    AVG(CAST((contract_win_rate_output."WIN_RATE_ESTIMATE") AS DOUBLE PRECISION)) AS average_of_win_rate_estimate_2
FROM mlp_prod.public.contract_win_rate_output  AS contract_win_rate_output
WHERE (contract_win_rate_output."RFP_LANE_ID" ) = 2508383 AND (contract_win_rate_output."INPUT_FILENAME" ) = 'cwr_csv_13318_1673975110.csv' AND ((( contract_win_rate_output."LOADED_AT"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2023-01-17 13:05') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( contract_win_rate_output."LOADED_AT"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('minute', 1, TO_TIMESTAMP('2023-01-17 13:05')) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1,
    2) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 500 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank
